name: The world want to tell you

metadata.name: The WAR Never ENDs
metadata.description:
The WAR Never ENDs
it happens all the time
You just don't see
It might be invisible
but it still remains
I just wondered
What do we get from war?
What are we fighting for?
If happiness is what we need
The peaceful world we want to see
peace and unity
I don't want it to be just a dream
...
PS.
Only the DEAD Have Seen the END of WAR
...
peace
